#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn24.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Hoticanacahotitathāgatosutta"
msgstr "17. A Realized One Both Exists and Doesn’t Exist"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.216"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn24.17:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn24.17:1.2"
msgid "“Kismiṃ nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kiṃ upādāya, kiṃ abhinivissa evaṃ diṭṭhi uppajjati:"
msgstr "“Mendicants, when what exists, because of grasping what and insisting on what, does the view arise:"

msgctxt "sn24.17:1.3"
msgid "‘hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā’”ti?"
msgstr "‘A Realized One both exists and doesn’t exist after death’?” …"

msgctxt "sn24.17:1.4"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn24.17:1.5"
msgid "niyato sambodhiparāyano”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn24.17:1.6"
msgid "Sattarasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
